description:
*** Private Equity news, personalized for you ***

Palico News is your personalized roundup of what’s happening in Private Equity and is brought to you by Palico, the first regulated online platform connecting the global Private Equity community.

PE NEWS FROM 50+ PUBLICATIONS

Every day, our data specialists sort and summarize articles from 50+ online publications covering the most important topics in Private Equity.

PERSONALIZED NEWS SELECTION

Personalize your news feed by region and investment strategy to receive only the news that matter to you.

EASILY READ AND SHARE ARTICLES

Read all the latest news or browse by category: Funds, Deals, Portfolio Companies, and Firms & People.

Easily share news items with colleagues and clients.

7,800+ GENERAL PARTNER PROFILES

Access detailed company profiles on 7,800+ General Partners.

NEVER MISS CRITICAL NEWS

Set up alerts and receive notifications about firms you want to monitor.

----------------------------------------------------------------

Palico News is the mobile extension of the Palico Private Equity Community where over 6,000 Private Equity professionals in 70+ countries stay informed, search for investment opportunities, and build dealflow across fundraisings, secondaries, co-investments and services.
releaseNotes: Optimized for iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus
